{"tid":260031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多寶集運","createTime":"2017-05-27T11:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T20:16:29.000Z","uid":61403,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f06ded6c6f073a9e9bdca69a3c8b8631f7e685b","tid":260031,"uid":61403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T11:53:50.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過用多寶最後拎唔返件貨？我依家好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前都伏過3次，諗住用埋呢次就算，點知真係出左事<br />\n1.上年雙11淘寶，卡左個幾月，過埋雙12先拎得<br />\n2.集8樣野，應該係唔見左一樣，又卡左成個月，仲要係咁吹佢先寄落黎，最後件失件過左兩三個月先免費寄落黎<br />\n3.集個空箱7kg(6.x) ，第二次用順豐集個同款嘅大號箱，1.4kg<br />\n<br />\n本身今次諗住用順豐，但個店主好似話順豐唔寄得光碟先用多寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今次寄貴野先黎出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf07050ab35f722fe8e652f1ccaf706b05e3454","tid":260031,"uid":61403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:47:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea713a53901fc5c59b0e1a4ff8d10673351065dc","tid":260031,"uid":61403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1ad47b5c14027a2112e33287e1ecc5c821814d","tid":260031,"uid":74209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:34:22.000Z","msg":"樓主，用過多寶，不過都係四五件貨自取，2kg左右，平，未試過寄失，樓主唔好彩下次唔好大時大節集運吧"},{"pid":"0b04e10095c86c364930cab95dc5ec8891ff23e0","tid":260031,"uid":82291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:36:49.000Z","msg":"用開多寶，又快又平<br />\n有埋自取車勁方便<br />\n未試過唔見野"},{"pid":"ad4e646de3f25e9099c8f3e19128280f4a45b81d","tid":260031,"uid":34626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:42:15.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾多寶 唔見我野仲del鳩我留言"},{"pid":"cb721a3471681ebdb4e2fd54e396e50c56028a8d","tid":260031,"uid":61403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T14:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用開多寶，又快又平<br />\n有埋自取車勁方便<br />\n未試過唔見野</blockquote><br />\n之後都係用順豐算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多寶多數都呃秤（就算唔係體積重都係）<br />\n順豐都係首重貴d"},{"pid":"c982a5c0d7855d2bc369bd9325d3bac4766120a2","tid":260031,"uid":9346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T14:13:53.000Z","msg":"等成個幾月都肯，你真係好人<br />\n佢開鋪無耐用過，以後永不錄用"},{"pid":"7f823b04d0a3c57d451f9c14733a270b1d8d1d3e","tid":260031,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T14:17:01.000Z","msg":"伏咁多次都仲用<br />\n你嗰到得順豐同多寶？"},{"pid":"54e676f6867260bc2b447dba0bd11e8906e03459","tid":260031,"uid":61403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T14:29:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>伏咁多次都仲用<br />\n你嗰到得順豐同多寶？</blockquote><br />\n基本上係<br />\n仲有自提櫃，但未用過"},{"pid":"07e4e7fa4f3a2931e63ed428a52c300808ccd12c","tid":260031,"uid":82291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T01:33:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用開多寶，又快又平<br />\n有埋自取車勁方便<br />\n未試過唔見野</blockquote><br />\n之後都係用順豐算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多寶多數都呃秤（就算唔係體積重都係）<br />\n順豐都係首重貴d</blockquote><br />\n我都試過收體積重，本身5kg收左我10kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d616537d5d102e6626698bd2c3716c04dbce4c28","tid":260031,"uid":7700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T01:41:11.000Z","msg":"雙十一果次之後已經轉會"},{"pid":"89ed6e9fa708bb2f78a24240535a4e04e2d68d52","tid":260031,"uid":92769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T01:53:07.000Z","msg":"用左多寶年幾都未試過唔見野"},{"pid":"ff32caec2b768daeffab2bccd207030672ddd868","tid":260031,"uid":116131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T19:35:42.000Z","msg":"屯門想轉會有咩方面又抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8720a65695a520e58940bb405fdff4d2968d7500","tid":260031,"uid":118915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T20:16:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雙十一果次之後已經轉會</blockquote><br />\n轉左邊度"}]}